OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FMore than three years after the event,
OL,7,Fthe chief executive only recently
OL,8,Fdiscovered Emily had been sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted in one of their hotel rooms,
OL,10,Fas Correspondent Ashna Hurynag reports
OL,12,FThe survivor of a sexual assault that
OL,13,Fhappened in a Travelodge hotel room
OL,14,Fthat her attacker had managed to gain
OL,15,Fa key to, has expressed her despair
OL,16,Fand cast doubt over the whether
OL,17,Fsecurity policies will improve
OL,18,Ffollowing her experience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
