OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FIt comes as Good Morning Britain and
OL,7,FITV News learnt that the survivor,
OL,8,F'Emily', whose name we have changed,
OL,9,Fwrote directly to the chief executive
OL,10,Fof the hotel chain in January 2023.
OL,12,FIn an email sent just over two weeks
OL,13,Fafter the incident at the Maidenhead
OL,14,Fhotel branch, the survivor details the
OL,15,Fhorrors of that night and appeals
OL,16,Fdirectly to CEO Jo Boydell to
OL,17,Finvestigate, saying the hotel in
OL,18,Fquestion "has completely failed at
OL,19,Fsafeguarding".
OL,26,@zD@JOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FThe letter sent on January 3 was
OL,7,Ftitled "Serious complaint" and despite
OL,8,Fbeing sent to Ms Boydell's personal
OL,9,Femail address, is understood to have
OL,10,Fbeen picked up by a member of her team
OL,11,Fand "handled on her behalf" according
OL,12,Fto Travelodge.
OL,14,FMs Boydell says she did not see the
OL,15,Femail, nor was it escalated to her.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@ZO]sD@EOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
