OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FMore than three years after the event,
OL,7,Fthe chief executive only recently
OL,8,Fdiscovered Emily had been sexually
OL,9,Fassaulted in one of their hotel rooms.
OL,11,FIn an interview with Good Morning
OL,12,FBritain, broadcast this week, Ms
OL,13,FBoydell makes it clear she only found
OL,14,Fout about the incident in early March,
OL,15,Fafter another news organisation
OL,16,Falerted her to it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FShe told me: "I first found out about
OL,7,Fthe details of the case when it was
OL,8,Freported by the BBC, and that's one of
OL,9,Fthe issues that's very clear to us. It
OL,10,Fabsolutely should not have been the
OL,11,Fcase and we made mistakes. And that's
OL,12,Fpart of the review to understand why
OL,13,Fit took so long."
OL,15,FBut I have uncovered a further email
OL,16,Fexchange between the survivor and
OL,17,Fmembers of staff working in the 'Chief
OL,18,FExecutive Office'.
OL,26,@nD@NOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FIt highlights the incident was raised
OL,7,Fwith the "Hotel Management team" and
OL,8,Fthat there was found to be "no
OL,9,Fbreakdown in procedure".
OL,11,FIn an email sent to the survivor on
OL,12,FJanuary 18, 2023, a staff member whose
OL,13,Fsignature says she works in the 'Chief
OL,14,FExecutive Office' explains that the
OL,15,Fhotel chain "investigated this matter
OL,16,Fwith both our Hotel and District
OL,17,FManagers".
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@`O]pD@\OUqD@WO]wD@MOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FShe says "no step had been missed in
OL,7,Fthe process" and there was "not one
OL,8,Fpart of the proceedings that they had
OL,9,Fnot followed correctly".
OL,11,FShe further tells the survivor: "The
OL,12,Fteam member's actions were completely
OL,13,Fcompliant."
OL,15,FMore than one email - feels to Emily -
OL,16,Flike more than one opportunity to act
OL,17,Fon the assault.
OL,26,@nD@JOUoD@LO]oD@\OUsD@aOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,F"I think that perhaps she (the CEO)
OL,7,Fdidn't see the email I sent to her
OL,8,Fpersonal email address, because I
OL,9,Fimagine she probably has quite a few
OL,10,Femails coming through," Emily tells me.
OL,12,F"But I really don't know how, you
OL,13,Fwouldn't know if you've got people in
OL,14,Fyour complaints department, in your
OL,15,Fchief executive's office, dealing with
OL,16,Femails on your behalf, how you don't
OL,17,Fknow at that point."
OL,19,FThe hotel strenuously deny this and
OL,20,Fsay categorically, the incident only
OL,21,Fcame to the CEO's attention last month.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@[pmnD@cpnrD@WO]tD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
