CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FSince then, they have made immediate
OL,7,Fchanges to the room access policy and
OL,8,Fhave commissioned an independent
OL,9,Freview to look at room-security and
OL,10,Faddress how serious customer incidents
OL,11,Fare managed.
OL,13,FWhen asked if Ms Boydell is the right
OL,14,Fperson to enact the changes in policy,
OL,15,FEmily is adamant "not anymore".
OL,26,@wD@ROUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FOtherwise, she says: "You would have
OL,7,Fdone more in a month, and you would
OL,8,Fhave said more. I mean, they have so
OL,9,Fmany hotels that if safety isn't top
OL,10,Fof the priorities, then they need to
OL,11,Flook at their top people."
OL,13,FTravelodge has always acknowledged
OL,14,Fthere were serious failures in their
OL,15,Fhandling of Emily's case and that
OL,16,Ftheir response was inappropriate.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
