PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,FJo Boydell, CEO of Travelodge, told
OL,7,FITV News: "I am deeply sorry for the
OL,8,Fdistress experienced by the survivor
OL,9,Fand I apologise for our handling of
OL,10,Fwhat happened to her. I have been very
OL,11,Fclear there were serious failures in
OL,12,Four handling of every aspect of our
OL,13,Fresponse to her. The email sent by the
OL,14,Fsurvivor in January 2023 was handled
OL,15,Fon my behalf and I am clear this
OL,16,Fshould never have happened.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,F"Our response was deeply inappropriate
OL,7,Fand our processes did not work as they
OL,8,Fshould have done in this instance
OL,9,Fbecause what happened was not
OL,10,Fescalated to me. Since I became aware
OL,11,Fof what happened, we have conducted an
OL,12,Finternal review and made immediate
OL,13,Fchanges to both our room security
OL,14,Fprocesses for additional key cards as
OL,15,Fwell as our review and escalation
OL,16,Fprocesses. I have commissioned an
OL,17,Findependent review led by a leading KC
OL,18,Fwhich is looking at every aspect of
OL,19,Four handling of this case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775268200
OL,3,CSurvivor of sexual assault has 'no
OL,4,Cfaith' Travelodge will change
OL,6,F"The safety and security of guests in
OL,7,Four hotels is my absolute priority. My
OL,8,Ffocus is on putting this right, on
OL,9,Flearning from what happened and making
OL,10,Fchanges to ensure our hotels are safe,
OL,11,Fand feel safe, for our customers."
OL,13,FThey have always maintained that the
OL,14,Fsecurity of guests in their hotels is
OL,15,Ftheir priority.
OL,17,FThey want everyone to feel safe, but
OL,18,Ffor Emily it's too late.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
